reviewText: It doesn't play in any thing, what apiece of wasted money
This may be a good lesson CD, but I have had so many problems trying to play it that I have given up. I can put 25 CD's or DVD's in my D drive and they play, not this one.

I put 3 stars because I got some good stuff from this DVD the missing two is because some of the licks are recycled licks with slightly variations from one version to the other, some sound like country music and others are kind of very basic.  Search in youtube, truefire uploaded three or four lessons out from this dvd.
